column2: b'The iDOLM@STER Cinderella Girls: Starlight Stage - 5th Anniversary! "Go Just Go!" PV'

b'An animated commercial by CloverWorks promoting the THE iDOLM@STER: Cinderella Girls - Starlight Stage (iOS/Android game)\'s fifth anniversary. The commercial features an animated music video of the song "Go Just Go!" which was released for the game\'s anniversary. '
[b'The iDOLM@STER Cinderella Girls: Anytime, Anywhere with Cinderella.']
